Description:
Attention first home buyer, investors and downsizes.
This attractive private residence provides a low maintenance lifestyle ideal for downsizing, first home buyers and investors. This neat and tidy two bedroom unit will impress you with its great sense of relaxed serenity and its excellently well maintained gardens.
Offering open plan living with dining, lounge & kitchen, two spacious bedrooms with built in robes, separate bath and shower, toilet, laundry, gas heating and split system heating & cooling. You will be impressed with the neat kitchen complete with gas cooker and good storage space. The home has been freshly painted with new flooring throughout the home. Sliding doors leading onto a private outdoor entertaining area, single lock up garage and off-street parking available. Ideally located close to schools, shops and transport this is a home you will be proud of. A must inspect at this price.

Description:
Tastefully renovated, quiet street
This home would make the perfect start for a first home buyer or investor, with a potential rental income of $250/wk. Just move straight in, there is really nothing you need to do, the present owner has done all the hard work tastefully renovating in neutral and warm tones throughout. Comprising formal lounge with floating floors, ceiling fan and airconditioner. The kitchen/dining has been updated and has a gas upright stove. The three bedrooms are all a good size, each with built in robes, master with an airconditioner. The renovated bathroom has a separate shower and bath and vanity with semi-recessed basin. There is ducted heating throughout and an instant hot water service. Outdoors is a large yard with established trees and landscaped gardens, two rainwater tanks (5000 litre and 10,000 litre), side drive to a carport/pergola and a 1 steel colorbond garage (power connected). Allotment approximately 820sqm.

Description:
Wow - Nothing to do - Just move in
With modern updates added to this property over the past few years, all whom inspect will be impressed with the interior renovations and general appearance of this home. This home consists of
three bedrooms with BIR's (Bay window in Master), open plan lounge meals area, spacious family room with easy access to the outside undercover entertaining area. The Kitchen has been updated with s/s cooking appliances, dishwasher and new laminate bench tops. The bathroom is spacious in size, including bath, separate shower and vanity unit. The home consists of a two car lockable carport with roller doors as well as a spacious steel garage with room for cars and workshop. An additional feature is the movable bungalow which is currently being used as a teenagers retreat/bedroom. The property backs on to a large parkland reserve, giving the kids plenty of room to run and play. Located with close proximity to public transport, Newcomb Central, local schools and Newcomb Secondary College. This home is very neat and tidy with minimal gardening required and would be perfect for a developing family through to property investors.
